					<h2>We recycle 90% of our tyres</h2>
					<p>Black ‘n’ Rounds recycle 90% of the tyres we recover through our facility. We currently use <a href="http://www.sussextyres.co.uk/" target="_blank">Pountney Tyres</a>, a family run business, to recycle 90% of the tyres we recover from our facility.</p>
