					<p>Secondly, we have a very large and powerful tyre shredding machine. Our tyres are shredded and sent for use in cement kilns. Our shred can go all over the world but most of the shred will be used in the UK. Tyres burn at 1,500 degrees and are much more cost effective than coal, and, when they burn, they are less damaging to the environment.</p>
